# W0PIUM — Project Overview

Private invite-only social network. Live at https://w0pium.walfir.com
Hosted on Synology NAS via Docker + Cloudflare Tunnel.
Repo: `\\MedSkin\docker\w0pium\`

## Stack

| Layer     | Tech                                                        |
|-----------|-------------------------------------------------------------|
| Backend   | Node.js 20 / Express 4 — single file `server.js` (~2500+ lines) |
| Database  | better-sqlite3 (synchronous SQLite, no ORM)                 |
| Frontend  | Vanilla JS SPA — no React, no TypeScript — single file `public/app.js` (~5000+ lines) |
| Realtime  | Server-Sent Events (`/api/events`)                          |
| Auth      | Session cookie (`httpOnly`, `sameSite: lax`)                |
| Email     | Resend API via native `fetch()`                             |
| Files     | Multer → local disk under `DATA_DIR/`                       |
| PWA       | Web App Manifest + Service Worker                           |
| Deploy    | Docker Compose + Cloudflare Tunnel (`w0pium-nas-2`)         |

## Key Files

```
server.js                   # ALL backend: routes, DB logic, migrations
public/app.js               # ALL frontend: router, pages, SSE client
public/pages/chat.js        # Chat page (voice, media gallery, search)
public/pages/drops.js       # Drops page (IntersectionObserver, views)
public/style.css            # CSS vars (dark default) + .light overrides
public/index.html           # SPA shell — one page, no framework
data/w0pium.db              # SQLite DB (git-ignored, live data)
.env                        # Secrets — never commit, never edit without confirmation
docker-compose.yml          # Docker Compose config
Dockerfile                  # Node 20 image, npm ci --omit=dev --ignore-scripts && npm rebuild
```

